<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about 我的诗词)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/cat_wo-de-shi-ci.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Jul 2017 09:34:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>与生共勉</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/yu-sheng-gong-mian/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;手游穷三代，追剧毁一生。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;闲聊难休止，安睡若高僧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;时光分秒过，不与世人争。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;求学无捷径，功到自然成。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/yu-sheng-gong-mian/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 20 Jun 2017 14:42:28 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>悼别外祖母</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/dao-bie-wai-zu-mu/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;寒风送柳泛轻尘，清明未至别故人。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;心向往昔花失宠，情到痛时雨亦真。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;云中哀乐声声起，梦里忧思处处闻。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;黑纱有泪归碧海，白发无心守空门。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>我的诗词</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/dao-bie-wai-zu-mu/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Mar 2017 04:12:21 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>